summary: This mod adds in your own little realm complete with your own house, guards, citizens, swimming pool and many other things.
descriptionHtml: hey guys, as this is one of my first mods it might be a bit buggy, do just tell me if you find any. This mod gives you your own little personal realm for you to live in. it comes complete with your own house, personal guards, citizens (merchants, beggars etc,), a public swimming pool, tavern, pet giant rat and stables. just tell me if you want anything else added in and i will try my best to add it in.
author: fartykis
